privacy policy
We do not provide any personally identifiable information to third parties.

We will pay the latest attention to the management of personal information and handle it as listed below.

Data analysis
In order to improve the convenience of the application, we pay the latest attention to the extent that we cannot anonymously identify individuals and perform access analysis.
For example, when the app crashes, we anonymously send the cause of the crash to help you fix the bug quickly.

Disclaimer
We provide as much support as possible for problems and inconveniences in use, but the developer shall not be liable for any damage caused by the user using this application.

